<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-6);">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
        <h1 style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">
            <%= t('join_family') %>
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--text-soft); line-height: 1.6;">
            Activities are open and accessible. You decide the value at the end.<br>
            <strong>Like a Free Tour, but for community.</strong>
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Simple How It Works -->
    <div
        style="background: var(--primary-light); padding: var(--space-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: var(--space-8); text-align: center; border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">How it works</h3>
        <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-5);">
            <div class="card" style="border: none; background: white;">
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">üìÖ</div>
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">1. Pick an activity</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-soft);">Browse the calendar and reserve your spot</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" style="border: none; background: white;">
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">ü§ù</div>
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">2. Show up & connect</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-soft);">Meet the community and enjoy the experience</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" style="border: none; background: white;">
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">üíõ</div>
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">3. Contribute by will</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-soft);">Pay what feels right at the end</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">Quick Questions</h2>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3); padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Do I need to pay upfront?</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-soft);">No. All activities are free to join. At the end, you contribute what you
                think is fair.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3); padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Can I come alone?</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-soft);">Absolutely! Most people come solo. That's the whole point‚Äîmaking new
                friends.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3); padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">What if I can't make it?</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-soft);">Just let us know. No penalties, no stress. We just need to know for the
                group size.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3); padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">How do I stay updated?</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-soft);">Join our WhatsApp group or follow us on Instagram for announcements and
                last-minute plans.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Social CTAs -->
    <div
        style="text-align: center; margin-top: var(--space-8); padding: var(--space-6); background: #fef9f3; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px dashed var(--primary);">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">Stay Connected</h3>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-3); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="https://wa.me/YOUR_WHATSAPP_NUMBER" target="_blank" class="btn"
                style="background: #25D366; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.2);">
                <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">üí¨</span> WhatsApp Group
            </a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/murciawelcomesyou" target="_blank" class="btn"
                style="background: #E4405F; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(228, 64, 95, 0.2);">
                <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">üì∏</span> Instagram
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
<script>
    gsap.from(".animate-title", { opacity: 0, y: -20, duration: 1, ease: "power2.out" });
    gsap.from(".animate-subtitle", { opacity: 0, y: -10, delay: 0.2, duration: 1 });
</script>